general.description: ALLWISE catalog: https://wise2.ipac.caltech.edu/docs/release/allwise/. For detailed descriptions of the columns see: https://wise2.ipac.caltech.edu/docs/release/allwise/expsup/sec2_1a.html

surveys.name: BHM
